  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unravel a Dark Family Secret<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247700/extras/b747123deeb67fe0207564ccf6f0aab8.avif?t=1729895591\" width=800 height=374 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as the only son of Johnathan Blackwood, and heir to the family legacy. After your father mysteriously disappears, you are forced to enter his study and soon uncover a maze of hidden rooms and cryptic puzzles that reveal your family’s dark secrets. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Experience Atmospheric Horror</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247700/extras/ee80925526af16c6e97de6249f2de655.avif?t=1729895591\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247700/extras_big/ee80925526af16c6e97de6249f2de655.avif?t=1729895591 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience immersive horror as you navigate through a labyrinthian manor filled with intricate puzzles and chilling atmospheres. Every shadow and every room could hold a clue or a threat. Decipher the clues left behind by your father and unlock the mysteries that will lead you to the truth.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Solve Twisted Puzzles</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247700/extras/f37e9ee035582c66157793e4e0337688.avif?t=1729895591\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247700/extras_big/f37e9ee035582c66157793e4e0337688.avif?t=1729895591 width=800 height=432 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover the secrets of Blackwood Manor by solving intricate, mind-bending puzzles woven into the fabric of the house itself. Every hidden chamber and ancient artifact holds a clue. Uncover the ritual tablets, align sacred symbols, and decipher cryptic riddles. With each puzzle solved, you’ll unlock deeper mysteries and draw closer to the truth.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Survive the Supernatural</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247700/extras/49c130500ea5c4bfd6645b5173ec4b72.poster.avif?t=1729895591\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247700/extras/49c130500ea5c4bfd6645b5173ec4b72.webm?t=1729895591\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247700/extras/49c130500ea5c4bfd6645b5173ec4b72.mp4?t=1729895591\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The dark being tied to your family is not just a memory. It lurks, waiting for a chance to break free. As you explore the manor, you must avoid its growing influence, gather items for protection, and use your wits to survive its ever-present danger.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unravel a Dark Family Secret<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247700/extras/b747123deeb67fe0207564ccf6f0aab8.avif?t=1729895591\" width=800 height=374 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as the only son of Johnathan Blackwood, and heir to the family legacy. After your father mysteriously disappears, you are forced to enter his study and soon uncover a maze of hidden rooms and cryptic puzzles that reveal your family’s dark secrets. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Experience Atmospheric Horror</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247700/extras/ee80925526af16c6e97de6249f2de655.avif?t=1729895591\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247700/extras_big/ee80925526af16c6e97de6249f2de655.avif?t=1729895591 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience immersive horror as you navigate through a labyrinthian manor filled with intricate puzzles and chilling atmospheres. Every shadow and every room could hold a clue or a threat. Decipher the clues left behind by your father and unlock the mysteries that will lead you to the truth.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Solve Twisted Puzzles</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247700/extras/f37e9ee035582c66157793e4e0337688.avif?t=1729895591\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247700/extras_big/f37e9ee035582c66157793e4e0337688.avif?t=1729895591 width=800 height=432 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover the secrets of Blackwood Manor by solving intricate, mind-bending puzzles woven into the fabric of the house itself. Every hidden chamber and ancient artifact holds a clue. Uncover the ritual tablets, align sacred symbols, and decipher cryptic riddles. With each puzzle solved, you’ll unlock deeper mysteries and draw closer to the truth.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Survive the Supernatural</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247700/extras/49c130500ea5c4bfd6645b5173ec4b72.poster.avif?t=1729895591\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247700/extras/49c130500ea5c4bfd6645b5173ec4b72.webm?t=1729895591\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247700/extras/49c130500ea5c4bfd6645b5173ec4b72.mp4?t=1729895591\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The dark being tied to your family is not just a memory. It lurks, waiting for a chance to break free. As you explore the manor, you must avoid its growing influence, gather items for protection, and use your wits to survive its ever-present danger.</p>",
